rComments: Grande professeur, classe génial, mais est pas un cours d'oiseau.

Guy est un des meilleurs professeurs de l'école de gestion Telfer. Il connait sa matière, a enseigné le cours 50 fois et ça parrait! Je recommande à tous de prendre un cours avec lui! Sympathique et drôle, Guy fait passer un cours de 3h TRÈS rapidement! Les notes de cours sont imprimées d'avance, et encourage donc la participation en classe.

One of the worst professors I've every had. He is stuck in the 80's all his course notes were created before the students in the class were born. Not clear what-so-ever on expectations and teaches Ads and Publicity methods from 30 years ago, more of a "history of ads and publicity" than anything else. Avoid at all cost.

Ottawa U has alot of awful teachers but Guy is the best teacher I've ever had. Funny, interesting, helpful, intelligent, he's the whole package, his exams are somewhat tough, his project is interesting, but the teacher himself, he's golden, you won't find any better teachers than him at Ottawa U. Take any class with him!
